                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 528.) I was in Smith-field—I heard a cry of "Stop thief," and saw the prisoner in custody of the prosecutor—I received these two shillings from the witnesses.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400817-name-748" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-748" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
