                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-748" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>MR. JOHN FIELD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am inspector of counterfeit coin to the Mint. These shillings are both counterfeit.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> It rained; I went into the house, and asked for half-a-pint of beer; I gave him the shilling; he said it was bad. I said, "Is it? I have got no more;" he gave it to me, and then he said, "Show it me again;" I did, and he said he would give me in charge.</p>
